{"tid":1300064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟日報：林鄭至今仍認為修例的初心，本質上並沒有任何錯誤","createTime":"2019-07-09T08:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T12:49:20.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f537cf1364418cc21fcc2beaa2655db051212b00","tid":1300064,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:58:05.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥今早出席暑假前最後一次行政會議前露面，公開強調《逃犯條例》修訂已「壽終正寢」。不過，民主派表明不收貨，認為有關字眼不夠正式，因根據立法會議事規則，是有「撤回」程序。<span style=\"color: red;\">到底林鄭月娥不願說「撤回」二字，所謂何事？</span><br />\n<br />\n觀乎政府由6月15日宣布「暫緩」修例後，林鄭月娥已多次用不同字眼表達《逃犯條例》修訂工作不會再進行，且字眼一次比一次強烈，由「已停止」到「完全停止」，再表明「自動失效」、「 will expire（將失效）」、「will die（將死亡）」，今日更宣布修例「壽終正寢」，「The Bill is dead（草案已死亡）」。<br />\n<br />\n有政界中人認為，在政治現實上「壽終正寢」，<span style=\"color: red;\">已比「撤回」更為嚴重，意味着條例不但不會在本屆立法會重新討論，連諮詢都不會再做</span>。林鄭本人也表明，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果單是「撤回」，其實三個月後也可在立法會「重推」</span>，指壽終正寢更「斬釘截鐵」地釋除疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n但既然如此，為何林鄭政府不索性宣布「撤回」？政界中人認為，<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭月娥至今仍認為政府修訂《逃犯條例》的「初心」，包括完善法制等，本質上並沒有任何錯誤，只是政府宣傳及表達手法不被市民接受，如現時宣布「撤回」，即等於變相承認《逃犯條例》不應該進行修訂，說法有違政府「初心」</span>，才難以宣之於口。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2395845/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2395845%2F&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7ItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=e9d47733\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2395845/</a>"},{"pid":"a51a0420b57f059b82e9e35cf04a9de9dd8e82e7","tid":1300064,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MOhOcPx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMOhOcPx.png&h=1844fc0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5885aa9b97520d16c655873d4dc61317540a1123","tid":1300064,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001ce58561a7576d7b8e6f244e79b52efbdd9b07","tid":1300064,"uid":189109,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:04:01.000Z","msg":"初你老母心咩，人地個女被你擺上枱過一棟，推唔到就用完即棄！你老母個臭閪有初心就同台灣傾單次移交啦冚家剷！<br />\n<br />\n不過我知你一定唔會咁做，咁做即係認咗根本唔洗推送中條例都可以解決件事"},{"pid":"f1dbe663af7ff08df2e43b80a4431cb32c6b96b3","tid":1300064,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:08:13.000Z","msg":"佢到宜家都堅持住個初心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n堅信做緊啱嘅嘢<br />\n咁強硬究竟係好事定壞事？"},{"pid":"b2db0032ffb4ca8ba9af85cd71fec62fb1adb6c3","tid":1300064,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:23:07.000Z","msg":"初心＝借人地個女過橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d71754147c9351123649b439ad91bd0ad622f7","tid":1300064,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb81233c4dd11f98dc861097c5fbf1d6ac6c03f","tid":1300064,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:42:17.000Z","msg":"23條直頭基本法寫明都撤得回<br />\n即係林鄭覺得自己大過基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e8d0bef2f9ce3e249fd04e99d48f851caa5e17","tid":1300064,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:57:23.000Z","msg":"即係19才子個講法<br />\n<br />\n林奠死要面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411994184c441b787e49bd99fe7cf1ceab18472f","tid":1300064,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:59:50.000Z","msg":"議事規則只有押後同撤回，係f唔會搵到暫緩同壽終正寢，宜家都仲係押後狀態。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbfca2c906a966642bdd4d8cbbbff31d14882865","tid":1300064,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b885e